’Ł@cd3d63cf9ca738b8094ec0dab41b81022237b90b2c87f3a422a87e1ddb2826eaŁųTitle: title: random bool
Path: Examples
Content:
Generate a random boolean value.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> random bool


```
Generate a random boolean value with a 75% chance of "true".
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> random bool --bias 0.75


```
